title: Fashion on POINT! with Brian "Q" Quinn | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 69
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!
Chrissy D is out sick this week babes!!!! Sal is joined by Q aka Brain Quinn from Impractical Jokers. The babes talk about their new favorite shows on Netflix. The fashion in Emily in Paris lures in Q and Sal is SHOCKED! Would you eat on the subway? Worst movies that you secretly love?! THE BABES ARE ALL OVER!
